body_html:
I had the same problem ; I swapped the order of the pull in tensorflow/workspace.bzl for the 3 instances of:
wget https://github.com/google/protobuf/archive/0b059a3d8a8f8aa40dde7bea55edca4ec5dfea66.tar.gz
wget http://mirror.bazel.build/github.com/google/protobuf/archive/0b059a3d8a8f8aa40dde7bea55edca4ec5dfea66.tar.gz

the mirror,bazel.build had the correct sha256sum but was second in the list. so swapping the order worked for me.
